{"id": "1222965272349249576", "channel_id": "1222965272349249576", "type": 0, "author_id": "960513153240825907", "author_name": "dyyqcwj", "author_bot": false, "content": "事实上面对这么一个BOSS自然是希洛莉莉队最佳，但是我作为正统毒队玩家面对这么一个BOSS也是手感火热。N的行动后果几乎能够承受，只需要特殊造物的帮助就能让阿格里帕拿下他！没错就是白面，加强之后高达35狂气配合关卡造物直接4费满狂，解决了生存问题，脐带自然是急需品之一，娃娃则是给到一个容错机会，但是最不起眼的仪式鸟更是帮助输出的核心。N召唤4个分身，仪式鸟一偷就是96力量（60级守秘人），其他的就是算力造物了，事实上距离最佳造物搭配还缺了一个水手哨，不过问题不大。队伍搭配也有优化空间，比如莉莉的灵魂诞生可以优化成珊瑚女之类的，总之是很快乐的350分了！", "timestamp": "2024-03-28T17:47:22.524000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 5}, {"emoji": "🛐", "emoji_id": null, "count": 4}], "attachments": [{"id": "1222965272659496970", "filename": "Screenshot_20240328_212355_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 181445, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1222965272349249576/1222965272659496970/Screenshot_20240328_212355_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg?ex=69fb7eaa&is=69fa2d2a&hm=3db1985c99c40978f38b8ca991acfbcf7d03f76cdab56a1e4207aeaa0f9b3abf&"}, {"id": "1222965273313677322", "filename": "Screenshot_20240328_175123_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 297321, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1222965272349249576/1222965273313677322/Screenshot_20240328_175123_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg?ex=69fb7eaa&is=69fa2d2a&hm=f52d12095de13328c2bd05a219428ab2995996ae354a3a811f3b532e1dd74be9&"}, {"id": "1222965273804673044", "filename": "Screenshot_20240329_004619_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 153729, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1222965272349249576/1222965273804673044/Screenshot_20240329_004619_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg?ex=69fb7eaa&is=69fa2d2a&hm=4122b4787fb730dbfe9996b116f275562e6682901dcd1cf5c829a38cd37b10af&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1222965272349249576", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "新融灾禁区5-3蜘蛛队打法", "forum_channel_id": "1